{"tid":1613491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信答謝印尼記者姐姐，民主女神像團隊手抄幫你寄","createTime":"2019-10-02T14:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T04:16:09.000Z","uid":190181,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cf19cb181119abc8310ba5748518b840dfd28fe5","tid":1613491,"uid":190181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"香港人一定要聲援印尼記者姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢為左報道香港既民主運動走到前線，同時因為香港人監管政府不力而產生既警暴受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以其實我地對佢既受傷都有責任!<br />\n<br />\n慰問又好，打氣又好，我地香港人最少都應該為Veby Mega Indah姐姐做少少野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位去以下條link既google form留言，我地民主女神團隊會手抄一次各位既message，再送去印尼大使館及SUARA 報館<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n============<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nPzsaK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nPzsaK&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHXylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=1d8f489c\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nPzsaK</a></span><br />\n============<br />\n香港民主女神像TG: <a href=\"https://t.me/LadyLibertyHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLadyLibertyHK&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHXylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=525d6cb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/LadyLibertyHK</a>"},{"pid":"bbf2e3ba50de6b4f6ae0e5f4c1f88b110e70c23b","tid":1613491,"uid":190181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8191086a4165224deeea5465c2c8df5cfb7134","tid":1613491,"uid":72210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e